    "blackboard": "┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              PREP. + WHICH / WHOM (Relative Clauses)       │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                           │\n│  RULE:                                                    │\n│  物 → prep. + WHICH    人 → prep. + WHOM                  │\n│  ✗ prep. + that  (错误!)                                  │\n│                                                           │\n│  三步法：                                                  │\n│  ①找动词 → ②定介词 → ③提前                                 │\n│                                                           │\n│  VERB + PREP. 参考表：                                     │\n│  talk about → about which    depend on → on which         │\n│  deal with → with which      turn to → to which           │\n│  work with → with whom       agree on → on which          │\n│                                                           │\n│  ⚠ set up 中的 up 是副词，不可提前！                        │\n│                                                           │\n│  学生例句区：                                               │\n│  \"The Forbidden City, in which 24 emperors lived...\"      │\n└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘",
