        "content": "【PPT 04 转换练习（5题，主动转被动）】\n\n【教师台词】\"Convert these active sentences to present perfect passive.\"\n\n1. The internet has changed Jan's life.\n2. Online communities have helped millions of people.\n3. Someone has updated the website.\n4. The company has added new safety features.\n5. People have shared Jan's story across the world.\n\n▲ 学生独立完成4分钟。\n\n【预设答案】\n1. Jan's life HAS BEEN CHANGED by the internet.\n2. Millions of people HAVE BEEN HELPED by online communities.\n3. The website HAS BEEN UPDATED.\n4. New safety features HAVE BEEN ADDED by the company.\n5. Jan's story HAS BEEN SHARED across the world.\n\n【易错点提醒】①第1题 life是单数→HAS been changed；②第2题 millions是复数→HAVE been helped；③been不要写成being！\n\n【PPT 05 辨析填空（5题，选正确时态）】\n\n【教师台词】\"Choose the correct form: past simple passive, present perfect passive, or present continuous passive.\"\n\n1. The app ______ (download) by 5 million users so far. → has been downloaded (so far=到现在)\n2. The website ______ (hack) last night. → was hacked (last night=具体过去时间)\n3. New features ______ (add) to the app right now. → are being added (right now=此刻)\n4. Jan's story ______ (share) by people in 50 countries. → has been shared (by people in 50 countries=到目前为止)\n5. The old website ______ (take down) two years ago. → was taken down (two years ago=具体过去时间)\n\n【差异化提示】A班可增加自由造句；B班重点辨析\"有具体过去时间→一般过去\"vs.\"没有具体时间+影响现在→现在完成\"。"
