    "blackboard": "┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│        PRESENT PERFECT PASSIVE VOICE                      │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                           │\n│  FORM: have/has + been + V3(过去分词)                     │\n│                                                           │\n│  THREE PASSIVE FORMS:                                     │\n│  一般过去：was/were + V3           \"was done\"             │\n│  现在完成：have/has + been + V3    \"has been done\"        │\n│  现在进行：am/is/are + being + V3  \"is being done\"        │\n│                                                           │\n│  ⚠ been (完成) ≠ being (进行)                             │\n│  ⚠ 有具体过去时间 → 一般过去时被动                         │\n│    无具体时间+影响现在 → 现在完成时被动                    │\n│                                                           │\n│  例：The app HAS BEEN DOWNLOADED by millions.             │\n│      Our lives HAVE BEEN CHANGED by the internet.         │\n└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘",
    "exercises": "【基础作业】（全体必做）\nI. 将下列主动句改为现在完成时被动句：\n1. The internet has changed our lives.\n2. Online communities have supported millions of users.\n3. Someone has hacked the website.\n4. The company has launched a new app.\n5. People have shared her story worldwide.\n\nII. 选择正确的被动形式（一般过去/现在完成/现在进行）：\n6. The website ______ (update) last week. → was updated\n7. The app ______ (download) over 10 million times so far. → has been downloaded\n8. The system ______ (test) right now. → is being tested\n9. New safety rules ______ (make) recently. → have been made\n10. The old platform ______ (shut down) in 2020. → was shut down\n\n【提高作业】（A班必做，B班选做）\nIII. 写3个句子，描述互联网如何改变了你的生活，使用现在完成时被动语态。\n\n【参考答案——教师用】\nI. 1. Our lives HAVE BEEN CHANGED by the internet.\n   2. Millions of users HAVE BEEN SUPPORTED by online communities.\n   3. The website HAS BEEN HACKED.\n   4. A new app HAS BEEN LAUNCHED by the company.\n   5. Her story HAS BEEN SHARED worldwide.\nII. 6. was updated  7. has been downloaded  8. is being tested\n    9. have been made  10. was shut down\nIII. 评分标准：①语法正确（have/has+been+V3）②内容相关③词汇使用。示例：My study habits have been changed by online courses. My social life has been enriched by social media. My privacy has been threatened by data collection.",
